01:23.616 --> 01:26.418
She's doomed.

01:26.486 --> 01:29.921
Louie, I know
      where this woman is.

01:29.989 --> 01:31.623
It's right near the farm

01:31.691 --> 01:34.993
where Simka and I
buy our goat knuckles.

01:35.060 --> 01:36.327
Oh, oh, oh...

01:36.395 --> 01:39.131
Well, maybe you can do
        something with this cab.

01:39.198 --> 01:41.465
I'll, I'll take a look.

01:41.533 --> 01:44.002
(starter cranking,
        engine stalling)

01:46.272 --> 01:49.006
Oh, I think I know
what the problem is.

01:49.074 --> 01:50.141
What?

01:50.209 --> 01:51.943
Winter.

01:52.011 --> 01:54.412
(wind howling)

01:54.479 --> 01:57.515
It's a very simple
                  choice, Latka.

01:57.583 --> 01:59.885
Either you have sex with me
         or you freeze to death.

01:59.952 --> 02:03.587
Sex. Death.

02:03.655 --> 02:05.756
Sex. Death.

