Hmm.

02:10.961 --> 02:14.633
Why don't you tell me
a little bit about yourself?

02:14.700 --> 02:18.603
It-it happened when Cindy and I
were waiting to be rescued.

02:18.670 --> 02:19.771
Yeah?

02:19.839 --> 02:20.972
