         just so you should feel

02:34.186 --> 02:36.287
a little less guilty. I mean,
        th-the bigger thing here

02:36.355 --> 02:37.722
is to, is to spare Simka.

02:37.790 --> 02:39.557
Yes. That's right.

02:39.625 --> 02:43.328
The only decent thing
to do is to deceive her.

02:43.395 --> 02:44.563
Whew!

02:46.565 --> 02:48.165
(door opening)

02:48.233 --> 02:50.635
Hi, honey. I'm home.

02:50.703 --> 02:53.305
Latka, I am so happy, I...

02:53.372 --> 02:56.641
