                  another woman!

02:59.045 --> 03:01.512
I'm sorry I hurt you.

03:01.580 --> 03:03.514
We must go to the priest.

03:03.582 --> 03:06.017
You must confess your sin.

03:06.085 --> 03:10.988
And whatever he advises,
                   we must obey.

03:11.056 --> 03:15.660
And so, Simka, <i>nik-nik,</i>

03:15.728 --> 03:17.529
<i>Latka lavorshney.</i>

03:17.597 --> 03:21.532
So, Simka must sin
with someone Latka works with.

03:21.600 --> 03:23.168
You mean to tell me,

03:23.236 --> 03:25.770
